optimized_sql: WITH filtered_store AS (SELECT s_store_sk, s_zip FROM store), filtered_address AS (SELECT ca_address_sk, ca_zip FROM customer_address WHERE ca_state = 'KS'), zip_mismatch_pairs AS (SELECT s.s_store_sk, a.ca_address_sk FROM filtered_store s, filtered_address a WHERE substring(s.s_zip,1,5) <> substring(a.ca_zip,1,5)), filtered_fact_chain AS (SELECT ss_ext_sales_price, i_brand_id, i_brand, i_manufact_id, i_manufact, c_current_addr_sk, ss_store_sk FROM store_sales INNER JOIN date_dim ON ss_sold_date_sk = d_date_sk AND d_year = 1999 AND d_moy = 2 INNER JOIN item ON ss_item_sk = i_item_sk AND i_category = 'Shoes' INNER JOIN customer ON ss_customer_sk = c_customer_sk AND c_birth_month = 2 WHERE ss_wholesale_cost BETWEEN 76 AND 96), join_with_pairs AS (SELECT f.i_brand_id, f.i_brand, f.i_manufact_id, f.i_manufact, f.ss_ext_sales_price FROM filtered_fact_chain f INNER JOIN zip_mismatch_pairs z ON f.ss_store_sk = z.s_store_sk AND f.c_current_addr_sk = z.ca_address_sk) SELECT i_brand_id AS brand_id, i_brand AS brand, i_manufact_id, i_manufact, SUM(ss_ext_sales_price) AS ext_price FROM join_with_pairs GROUP BY i_brand, i_brand_id, i_manufact_id, i_manufact ORDER BY ext_price DESC, i_brand, i_brand_id, i_manufact_id, i_manufact LIMIT 100
